{"tid":619324,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［18dser請進］其實英文,又有咩好怕喎","createTime":"2018-04-06T13:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T14:19:09.000Z","uid":139484,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e49260e6cc1c702e67ef13e8095fad6ecd1ddbbb","tid":619324,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟係17dser,而且係band2尾中中出黎果種<br />\n之前係學術台見到好多人開post求改文<br />\n而小弟咁啱又有買卷<br />\n咁不如試下攞份真跡比連登學霸改啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/618092/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/618092/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/213909_240997de8d9b3bfc9adbb4d202f0eb70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F213909_240997de8d9b3bfc9adbb4d202f0eb70.png&h=ab3bbf79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/213911_d59951f3e55adb37959fbae36f38b0eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F213911_d59951f3e55adb37959fbae36f38b0eb.png&h=e3c65a44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/213912_38f89ee6018ae0d821e831712563991b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F213912_38f89ee6018ae0d821e831712563991b.png&h=616d709b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/213913_1519901668c6f6cc1e20b440deab0ce3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F213913_1519901668c6f6cc1e20b440deab0ce3.png&h=a0fb7ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到呢度,其實小弟都覺得巴打們意見幾中肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,咁grammatical mistakes柒左冇得否認,language流於淺薄都自己知衰,<del></del>雖然lvl3真係幾hurt下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到呢度,咁呢篇lvl3係考評局眼中係咩grade呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/214609_38dc5d17d0d8d90071fea0d8e5305221.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F214609_38dc5d17d0d8d90071fea0d8e5305221.png&h=b52df562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話呢,英文底子唔好/mock考衰左嘅18dser唔洗太驚<br />\n考評局改卷其實冇想象中咁harsh<br />\n連小弟咁嘅水平執到粒星<br />\n咁各位dser都唔好妄自菲薄<br />\n平常心就夠做了<br />\n最後祝各位18dser加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18d765c0084e286791be4257a3a6c19add08d0d","tid":619324,"uid":29566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:17:17.000Z","msg":"我反而唔明你篇文邊到唔好，係得language分數可能會低少少，content 同organization係非常出色咁對應返哂條題目要求你解決嘅問題，篇文睇得好舒服。"},{"pid":"c36efa80493bcd71085c55e3bd228342ea65c467","tid":619324,"uid":75500,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"連登仔都好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5413ec5db93e1ebdb23490c93600dbcad4e4fd1e","tid":619324,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"你已經好過好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11a0376cfa472a16432619082652423c0dca1ea","tid":619324,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d28419e1a832f89d13ac757ca210136620d725","tid":619324,"uid":77716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"難怪咁多人話DSE係用嚟削弱本地學生的競爭力&hellip;居然有咁多文法錯誤都可以有星&hellip;"},{"pid":"8e7b9b08148a26a